channel.title: Hard questions!
channel.description:
I've downloaded Allstar V2 source..
Everything works fine.. The only problem is I can't do pickup or xteleto/tome a mod!
What's the correct code to pickup and how do I tele a mod to me?
Another thing.. I knew there was some way of flying in allstar. Is it still possible? how?
Thanks you!

item.title: Hard questions!
item.dc:creator: @silabgarza silabgarza
item.description:
@silabgarza wrote:

in allstar
::pickup 00995 10000
to spawn items

::xteleto NAME
2 tele 2 people

::xteletome NAME
to teleport people to u

to fly
i think it has a command that is known as “god”
::god
